BLENDED WHISKIES

Here are the most popular of American whiskies. Year in and year out, they continue as favorites. All are skillful blends of aged pure whiskies with pure erain neutral spirits, which have no effect on the flavor other than to soften and attenuate it.

These whiskies, particularly in the lower price brackets, will be sharply affected by any ban on distillation.
